State of Connecticut v. Lueke Cooper (8476)

Daly, Nokcott and Heiman, Js.

Argued January 18 decision released February 5, 1991 Thomas C. C. Sargent, for the appellant (defendant). RichardF. Jacobson, assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were Donald A. Browne, state’s attorney, and Stephen J. Sedensky, assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (state). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
